methods.channelBuilder:
Creates a basic ManagedChannelBuilder by invoking
 Grpc.newChannelBuilder(String, ChannelCredentials) with DeephavenTarget.toString() and the
 appropriate CallCredentials.

:param target: (io.deephaven.uri.DeephavenTarget) - the Deephaven target
:return: (io.grpc.ManagedChannelBuilder<?>) the channel builder
